			<link><![CDATA[https://forum.dlrp.eu/forum/index.php?thread/10929-meine-bewerbung-als-probe-suporter/]]></link>
			<description><![CDATA[<strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Inhalts Verzeichniss: </span></span></span></u></strong><br><ul><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">OOC Informationen</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Stärken &amp; Schwächen</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Warum ich?</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Aktivität</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Kontaktmöglichkeiten </span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Schlusswort</span></span></span></li></ul>
<br><br><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">OOC Informationen :</span></span></span></u></strong><br><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ich heiße Marian und bin 15 Jahre alt. Gehe in die 9te Klasse. In meiner Freizeit Spiele ich gerne GTA RP, Apex Legends.</span></span></span><br><br><br><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,255,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"></span></span></span></u></strong>…]]></description>
			<pubDate>Tue, 12 Jul 2022 12:44:36 +0000</pubDate>
			<dc:creator><![CDATA[mrrn]]></dc:creator>
			<guid><![CDATA[https://forum.dlrp.eu/forum/index.php?thread/10929-meine-bewerbung-als-probe-suporter/]]></guid>
						<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Inhalts Verzeichniss: </span></span></span></u></strong></p><ul><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">OOC Informationen</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Stärken &amp; Schwächen</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Warum ich?</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Aktivität</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Kontaktmöglichkeiten </span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Schlusswort</span></span></span></li></ul>
<p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">OOC Informationen :</span></span></span></u></strong></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ich heiße Marian und bin 15 Jahre alt. Gehe in die 9te Klasse. In meiner Freizeit Spiele ich gerne GTA RP, Apex Legends.</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,255,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Stärken</span></span></span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"> &amp; </span></span></span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Schwächen</span></span></span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"> : </span></span></span></u></strong></p><ul><li><span style="color:rgb(0,255,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Hilfsbereit</span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(0,255,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span></span></span><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Zuverlässig</span><br><span style="font-size: 32px;"><strong></strong></span></span></span></li><li><span style="color:rgb(255,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Neugierig</span></span></span></li></ul><p><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style=""><br></span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Warum genau ich?</span></span></span></u></strong></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Ich finde, ich würde meine rolle als probe Supporter sehr gut meistern, weil ich sehr nett, zielstrebig bin. Ich bin auch Ehrgeizig, das Heist ich versuche bei allem das Beste zu geben. Ich habe auch sehr viel Spaß daran Menschen zu Helfen. Ich bin gut im organisieren von Sachen. </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Aktivität :</span></span></span></u></strong></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Montags - Donnerstags 16-22 Uhr </span><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span></span></span></span></span></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Freitags - Sonntags 13-open End Uhr</span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Kontaktmöglichkeiten :</span></span></span></u></strong><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;"></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Discord: Real_Mrrn#6271<br>Steam: Gejaxt`von`Mrrn </span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong><u><span style="color:rgb(0,0,0);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Schlusswort :</span></span></span></u></strong></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Liebes DLRP Team, vielen dank für eure Aufmerksamkeit. Ich würde mich natürlich sehr darüber freuen eine Positive Rückmeldung zu erhalten. <img src="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/2764.png" alt="&lt;3" title="heart" class="smiley" srcset="https://forum.dlrp.eu/images/smilies/emojione/2764@2x.png 2x" height="23" width="23" loading="eager"> </span></span></span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Mit Lieben Grüßen</span></span></span><span style="color:rgb(67,67,67);"><span style="font-family:Arial;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><span></span></span></span></span></p><p><br><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;">Marian</span></strong></p>]]></content:encoded>
